<br>
Alysia smiled as Hippolyte included the Ancients in her speach. Alysia then reached against her sides and removed her daggers keeping them well in her hands.<br>
<br>
She glanced into the woods and growled lowly to herself. She then turned her eyes back to her athelfi.<br>
<br>
&quot;I will be proud to once again ride with my sisters.&quot; She hadn't gone against a mortal enemy in a long time, Dawn was right. This was easy. Child's play. To Alysia, this would be fun. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~*~ Jessica ~*~<br>
